== Core features
X Open Mapfile template
X Add Mapfile to Map
X deal with multiple layers
X Fill combobox with existing MS layers
X Replace current Mapfile Layer
X auto-refresh layer
* layer property window
* select layers to display in layer property window
* Insert code snippets
* right-click on layer -> edit

== text editing
X Syntax coloring
X undo/redo support
* link to documentation
* block management
* comment / uncomment
* matching "end"
* Errors position and lines
* highlight deprecated

